#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pivot_table.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pivot\\_table"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:1 of
msgid "Create a spreadsheet-style pivot table as a DataFrame."
msgstr "创建一个电子表格风格的透视表作为 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:3 of
msgid ""
"The levels in the pivot table will be stored in MultiIndex objects "
"(hierarchical indexes) on the index and columns of the result DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"透视表中的层级将存储在结果 DataFrame 的索引和列上的 MultiIndex 对象（分层"
"索引）中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:8 of
msgid ""
"If an array is passed, it must be the same length as the data. The list "
"can contain any of the other types (except list). Keys to group by on the"
" pivot table index.  If an array is passed, it is being used as the same "
"manner as column values."
msgstr ""
"如果传递一个数组，它必须与数据长度相同。列表可以包含任何其他类型（除了"
"列表）。用于在透视表索引上分组的键。如果传递一个数组，它将以与列值相同的"
"方式使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:13 of
msgid ""
"If an array is passed, it must be the same length as the data. The list "
"can contain any of the other types (except list). Keys to group by on the"
" pivot table column.  If an array is passed, it is being used as the same"
" manner as column values."
msgstr ""
"如果传递一个数组，它必须与数据长度相同。列表可以包含任何其他类型（除了"
"列表）。用于在透视表列上分组的键。如果传递一个数组，它将以与列值相同的"
"方式使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:18 of
msgid ""
"If list of functions passed, the resulting pivot table will have "
"hierarchical columns whose top level are the function names (inferred "
"from the function objects themselves) If dict is passed, the key is "
"column to aggregate and value is function or list of functions."
msgstr ""
"如果传递函数列表，生成的透视表将具有分层列，其顶层是函数名称（从函数对象"
"本身推断）。如果传递字典，则键是聚合列，值是函数或函数列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:24 of
msgid ""
"Value to replace missing values with (in the resulting pivot table, after"
" aggregation)."
msgstr "用于替换缺失值的值（在聚合后的结果透视表中）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:27 of
msgid "Add all row / columns (e.g. for subtotal / grand totals)."
msgstr "添加所有行/列（例如用于小计/总计）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:29 of
msgid "Do not include columns whose entries are all NaN."
msgstr "不包括所有条目均为 NaN 的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:31 of
msgid ""
"Name of the row / column that will contain the totals when margins is "
"True."
msgstr "当 margins 为 True 时，包含总计的行/列的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:34 of
msgid "Specifies if the result should be sorted."
msgstr "指定结果是否应排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:37 of
msgid "An Excel style pivot table."
msgstr "一个 Excel 风格的透视表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.pivot`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:43 of
msgid "Pivot without aggregation that can handle non-numeric data."
msgstr "无需聚合即可处理非数值数据的透视操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:45 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.melt`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:46 of
msgid ""
"Unpivot a DataFrame from wide to long format, optionally leaving "
"identifiers set."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 从宽格式转换为长格式，可选择保留标识符集合。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`wide_to_long`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:49 of
msgid "Wide panel to long format. Less flexible but more user-friendly than melt."
msgstr "宽面板转为长格式。比 melt 更不灵活但更用户友好。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:52 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:76 of
msgid "This first example aggregates values by taking the sum."
msgstr "第一个示例通过求和来聚合值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:88 of
msgid "We can also fill missing values using the `fill_value` parameter."
msgstr "我们也可以使用 `fill_value` 参数来填充缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:100 of
msgid "The next example aggregates by taking the mean across multiple columns."
msgstr "下一个示例通过对多个列取平均值来进行聚合。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot_table.pivot_table:113 of
msgid ""
"We can also calculate multiple types of aggregations for any given value "
"column."
msgstr "我们还可以为任何给定值列计算多种类型的聚合。"

